message: Undid revision 1056832722 by [[Special:Contributions/Kansas Bear|Kansas Bear]] ([[User talk:Kansas Bear|talk]]) Restored information with source. User appears to be engaged in edit warring, in addition to violating WP:No personal attacks and WP:Assume good faith.
Undid revision 1056829953 by [[Special:Contributions/Kansas Bear|Kansas Bear]] ([[User talk:Kansas Bear|talk]]) Disruptive editing, restored information with source.

No source whatsoever claims that the French "came out triumphant". They were able to save their army, but the victory was costly and they were forced to abandon the booty. Furthermore, a biased editor visibly cherry-picked sources to magnify Italian casualties and minimize French casualties.
